pageProduct.name: SUP Focus 25 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Helps support energy generation & enhances cognitive performance.

STAY SHARP & PERFORM
If you are looking for more than coffee or energy drinks to perform in a fast-paced environment, look no further... SUP have developed a formula to support your energy production, mental clarity and performance. Brahmi and Gotu Kola have been traditionally used in Ayurvedic medicine to improve memory and cognition. 

WHY POP SUP? 
SUP Focus contains Vitamin B12&B6, American Ginseng and a hint of Caffeine to help: 
  • Enhance cognitive performance 
  • Improve mental alertness
  • Support energy generation
  • Support memory and cognitive function
POPSUP

Size: 25 Soft Capsules

KEY FEATURES

• Enhances cognitive performance
• Improves mental alertness
• Support energy generation
• Support memory and cognitive function

Warnings

Adults only. Contains 40mg of total caffeine per soft capsule. A cup of instant coffee contains approximately 80mg of caffeine. Caffeine intake more than 200mg per day is not recommended during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Limit the use of caffeine-containing products (including tea & coffee) when taking this product. Caffeine interacts with enzyme CYP1A2 in the liver. Consult your health professional before taking with other medicines. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Talk to an Ayurvedic practitioner/health professional if you are unsure if this medicine is right for you. Do not use product if tamper-evident seal is broken or missing. Store below 25oC. CONTAINS SOYA BEAN PRODUCTS AND SULFITES.

Ingredients

Bacopa monnieri (Brahmi) herb top extract dry conc. std. 75mg
- Equiv. to Bacopa monnieri herb top dry 2.85g (min.)
- Equiv. to total Bacosides calculated as bacoside A 37.5mg
Caffeine 40mg
Cantella asiatica (Gotu Kola) leaf extract dry conc. 20mg
- Equiv. to Centella asiatica leaf dry 200mg
Cyanocobalamin (Vitamin B12) 100micrograms
Ginkgo biloba (Ginkgo) leaf extract dry conc. std 58mg
- Equiv. to Ginkgo biloba leaf dry 2.61g (min.)
- Equiv. to Ginkgo flavonglycosides 14.21mg
- Equiv. to Ginkgolides and bilobalide 3.48mg
Lecithin 85.62mg
Panax quinquefolius (American Ginseng) root extract dry conc. 62.5mg
- Equiv. to Panax quinquefolius root dry 250mg
Pyridoxine hydrochloride 10mg
- Equiv. to Pyridoxine (Vitamin B6) 8.23mg

Allergen Contains: Soybean| Sulphites

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Gluten| Peanuts

Directions

Adults only. Take 1 soft capsule daily with food to support energy production & cognitive function. Take 2 soft capsules daily with food to help mental alertness.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
